## Harness Engineering 配套 Agent

本仓库采纳 [Harness Engineering 规范](harness-engineering/README.md) 的配套 Agent 套件。各 Agent 的输入输出契约与系统提示均在 `harness-engineering/agents/<name>/`，由工具按需加载。

| 阶段 | Agent | 入口 |
| --- | --- | --- |
| H1 | RequirementsInterviewer | `harness-engineering/agents/requirements-interviewer/AGENT.md` |
| H1↔H3 | RepoImpactMapper | `harness-engineering/agents/repo-impact-mapper/AGENT.md` |
| H3 | DesignReviewer | `harness-engineering/agents/design-reviewer/AGENT.md` |
| H4 | TestCaseAuthor | `harness-engineering/agents/test-case-author/AGENT.md` |
| H5 | CodingExecutor | `harness-engineering/agents/coding-executor/AGENT.md` |
| H5/H6 | CommitAuditor | `harness-engineering/agents/commit-auditor/AGENT.md` |
| H6 | ReleaseNoteWriter | `harness-engineering/agents/release-note-writer/AGENT.md` |
| 跨阶段 | DocGardener | `harness-engineering/agents/doc-gardener/AGENT.md` |

> 不要把上述 `AGENT.md` 的正文复制进本文件——`AGENTS.md` 是目录而非百科。
